/******************************************************
 OFFER ENGINE v5.4.1 - ORIGINAL WORKFLOW PATCHED
 -----------------------------------------------------
 Changes:
  - Creative offers solve to minimum 1.27 DSCR
  - Solver uses 1.275 DSCR buffer to avoid rounding misses
  - Primary and backup cannot differ only by balloon term
  - Backup prioritizes stronger CF / CoC / DSCR
  - Cash offer uses original ARV table
  - Cash MAO does NOT deduct repairs unless transcript/listing confirms repairs
  - Cash MAO does NOT deduct closing costs
  - Rehab / acquisition cost / seller agent fee shown for closer reference
  - Pass-through fields preserved for downstream nodes
******************************************************/

